        <li>Use the Software in compliance with applicable laws</li>
        <li>Not use the Software to harm, harass, or infringe on others' rights</li>
        <li>Be responsible for any content you create or actions you take using the Software</li>
        <li>Comply with the terms of service of any third-party providers you connect to</li>
